                            <comment id="17755762" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Fri, 18 Aug 2023 02:11:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I originally started working on reverting the change (apply it only in case of 403) and it seems that the &quot;error&quot; handling of JavabinTupleStreamParser is simply missing. this coupled with the fact that /select and /export actually have different response formats in case of exceptions makes it so that the &quot;/select and javabin&quot; workflow is not reflecting the error correctly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
